ser/l/000/46/04/460405.jpg?r=1601235205')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/460405\" class=\"l\">效坤诗迷</a>\n<small class=\"grey\"> 在玩 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-2-6 14:15</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">2026.2- 第三天 和炉石战棋比复杂太多 思考时间太短</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_47734666\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"719276\">\n<a href=\"/user/719276\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/71/92/719276.jpg?r=1732286127&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/719276\" class=\"l\">壹原</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars7\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-1-2 14:39</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">赌狗的荣光。\r\n当你遇到了一把极小概率的天胡局。每一次摸牌都很顺，每一次海克斯也很顺，你颅内的高朝到达了顶峰，你很沉迷于这种感觉。于是，你一次又一次打开游戏，进行对局，只为再经历那一次小概率事件，让你的大脑再爽一次。\r\n是的，这就是赌狗。\r\n这也是一种守株待兔，兔子极小概率得撞了柱子，你很爽，你想再体会一次这极小概率带来的快感，于是你守着柱子，赌了一天又一天。\r\n我深知这是一场挥霍时间与生命的无意义赌局，但我戒不掉。我戒不掉</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_46577719\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"ukinoshita\">\n<a href=\"/user/ukinoshita\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/76/38/763847.jpg?r=1753743662&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/ukinoshita\" class=\"l\">Ukino</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars7\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-7-20 17:28</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">消磨时间一大利器</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_41300944\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"868479\">\n<a href=\"/user/868479\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/86/84/868479.jpg?r=1720281127&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/868479\" class=\"l\">犹如神明般的你</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars6\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-5-24 02:19</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">运气游戏，上课玩挺合适</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_39940850\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"702969\">\n<a href=\"/user/702969\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/70/29/702969.jpg?r=1742572601&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/702969\" class=\"l\">Sakura</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars7\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-11-10 09:39</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">两把铲子一节课，六把铲子回宿舍</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_34676974\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"blackkeys\">\n<a href=\"/user/blackkeys\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/41/03/410371.jpg?r=1673342859&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/blackkeys\" class=\"l\">Op.10 No.5</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars6\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-10-12 14:39</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">总体同云顶，真要下棋也不太想在手机上玩</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_34084219\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"acla\">\n<a href=\"/user/acla\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/52/84/528476.jpg?r=1683373992&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/acla\" class=\"l\">Acla</a>\n<small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-7-10 22:34</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">玩了一下，跳脸活动太多，且新号大都是人机局，弃。\r\n感觉不如TFT。。。端游手游角色互通</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_32020522\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"zeeee\">\n<a href=\"/user/zeeee\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/68/12/681207.jpg?r=1674416084&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/zeeee\" class=\"l\">准时不早退的小黄前</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars3\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-6-16 21:37</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">垃圾游戏，每个版本都是玩一会就腻了。怀疑概率会随对局改动，有时开哪个羁绊来哪个羁绊的牌，有时牌死都不来</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_27375871\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"871913\">\n<a href=\"/user/871913\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/87/19/871913.jpg?r=1713713266&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/871913\" class=\"l\">gunnainai</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars8\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-4-21 23:45</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">虽说就是手机版云顶之弈，还和PC端不互通，但是玩了一段时间，包括过年复刻了天选福星让我回忆到了云顶最巅峰的赛季后，我觉得金铲铲这个运营做的还是比云顶要好不少</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_30369993\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"mybravely\">\n<a href=\"/user/mybravely\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/48/70/487096.jpg?r=1618566987')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/mybravely\" class=\"l\">水晶蜻蜓梦</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars1\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2024-4-13 19:09</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">马服特色魔改的移动端云顶之弈\r\n其好玩程度就像是在一碟香喷喷的菜上面浇上了一坨史\r\n那云顶就算再好玩我也只能给它史的评分了</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_30202898\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<template id=\"likes_reaction_grid_item\" type=\"text/template\">\n    <a class=\"item {selected_class}\"\n          href=\"javascript:void(0);\"\n          data-like-type=\"{type}\"\n          data-like-main-id=\"{main_id}\"\n          data-like-related-id=\"{related_id}\"\n          data-like-value=\"{value}\"\n          title=\"{users}\"\n          data-toggle=\"tooltip\">\n        <span cl